we are in tonight, to the generosity

00:42:01.720 --> 00:42:04.660
and commitment of extraordinary
women patrons.

00:42:04.660 --> 00:42:08.790
Mary Louise Curtis Bok established
the Curtis Institute in 1924.

00:42:08.790 --> 00:42:10.420
Later set up an endowment to pay

00:42:10.420 --> 00:42:14.900
in full tuition expense
for all Curtis students.

00:42:14.900 --> 00:42:18.940
