1925 paid for the construction

00:42:18.940 --> 00:42:23.870
of this hall, set up an endowment
to support free public concerts

00:42:23.870 --> 00:42:26.720
and commissions which
continue to this day.

00:42:26.720 --> 00:42:31.230
