00:42:37.290 --> 00:42:41.320
And also provided an endowment to
have them perpetually maintained

00:42:41.320 --> 00:42:44.760
and specifically performed
in concerts.

00:42:44.760 --> 00:42:49.220 position:56%
So, we're grateful to the Curtis
Institute for helping us be faithful

00:42:49.220 --> 00:42:53.650
to this bequest by playing
the Stradivarius instruments

00:42:53.650 --> 00:42:56.720
